P_HTM[6865]="*3. Suppaṭicchannasikkhāpada**3. The training rule on well-covered*";
P_HTM[6866]="*Tena samayena buddho bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme.**At one time the Buddha was staying at Sāvatthī in the Jeta Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s Monastery.*";
P_HTM[6867]="*Tena kho pana samayena chabbaggiyā bhikkhū kāyaṃ vivaritvā antaraghare gacchanti …pe….**At that time the monks from the group of six were walking in inhabited areas with their bodies uncovered. …*";
