P_HTM[6869]="*Suppaṭicchannena antaraghare gantabbaṃ.**One should be well-covered while walking in an inhabited area.*";
P_HTM[6870]="*Yo anādariyaṃ paṭicca kāyaṃ vivaritvā antaraghare gacchati, āpatti dukkaṭassa.**If a monk, out of disrespect, walks in an inhabited area with his body uncovered, he commits an offense of wrong conduct.*";
