P_HTM[7254]="*27. Sakkaccapaṭiggahaṇasikkhāpada**27. The training rule on receiving respectfully*";
P_HTM[7255]="*Tena samayena buddho bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme.**At one time the Buddha was staying at Sāvatthī in the Jeta Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s Monastery.*";
