P_HTM[7997]="*68. Chamāsikkhāpada**68. The training rule on the ground*";
P_HTM[7998]="*Tena samayena buddho bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme.**At one time the Buddha was staying at Sāvatthī in the Jeta Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s Monastery.*";
