P_HTM[10761]="*13. Ajjhokāsasallapanasikkhāpada**13. The training rule on talking out in the open*";
P_HTM[10762]="*Tena samayena buddho bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme.**At one time when the Buddha was staying at Sāvatthī in Anāthapiṇḍika’s Monastery,*";
