P_HTM[10774]="*“Yā pana bhikkhunī ajjhokāse purisena saddhiṃ ekenekā santiṭṭheyya vā sallapeyya vā, pācittiyan”ti.**‘If a nun stands or talks alone with a man out in the open, she commits an offense entailing confession.’”*";
