P_HTM[10779]="*Ajjhokāso nāma**Out in the open:*";
P_HTM[10780]="*appaṭicchanno hoti kuṭṭena vā kavāṭena vā kilañjena vā sāṇipākārena vā rukkhena vā thambhena vā kotthaḷiyā vā, yena kenaci appaṭicchanno hoti.**not concealed by a wall, a door, a screen, a cloth screen, a tree, a pillar, a grain container, or anything else.*";
