P_HTM[10782]="*manussapuriso, na yakkho na peto na tiracchānagato, viññū paṭibalo santiṭṭhituṃ sallapituṃ.**a human male, not a male spirit, not a male ghost, not a male animal. He understands and is capable of standing together and talking.*";
