P_HTM[14107]="*“kathañhi nāma bhikkhuniyo itthālaṅkāraṃ dhāressanti, seyyathāpi gihiniyo kāmabhoginiyo”ti.**“How can nuns wear jewellery? They are just like householders who indulge in worldly pleasures!”*";
