P_HTM[14110]="*“kathañhi nāma chabbaggiyā bhikkhuniyo itthālaṅkāraṃ dhāressantī”ti …pe…**“How can the nuns from the group of six wear jewellery?” …*";
P_HTM[14111]="*“saccaṃ kira, bhikkhave, chabbaggiyā bhikkhuniyo itthālaṅkāraṃ dhārentī”ti?**“Is it true, monks, that those nuns do this?”*";
