P_HTM[14507]="*tilatelaṃ sāsapatelaṃ madhukatelaṃ eraṇḍatelaṃ vasātelaṃ.**sesame oil, mustard seed oil, honey tree oil, castor oil, oil from tallow.*";
P_HTM[14508]="*Madhu nāma**Honey:*";
